## Frontend Pages & Routes

### Route Map

| URL | Page | Auth Required | Description |
|-----|------|:---:|-------------|
| `/` | Redirect | No | → `/login` if not logged in, → `/dashboard` if logged in |
| `/login` | login.html | No | Email/password login + Google OAuth button |
| `/signup` | signup.html | No | Registration form + Google OAuth |
| `/dashboard` | dashboard.html | ✅ | User's personal dashboard |
| `/admin` | admin.html | ✅ (admin JWT) | Admin panel |
| `/pay` | pay.html | ✅ | Razorpay checkout |

### Dashboard (Dynamic, Per-User)

The dashboard pulls data from the API using the logged-in user's session. It shows:

